result.name: Expression and Mutation Analysis of CDKN2B gene Implicated in Human and Canine Breast Cancer
result.description: A study on expression and mutation analysis of CDKN2B gene implicated in human and canine mammary tumors through real-time PCR and Sanger Sequencing. Forty mammary tumor and non-tumorous samples of female dog and women were analyzed during this research.
result.center: Institute of Biochemistry and Biotechnology, University of Veterinary & Animal Sciences, Pakistan
